items.name: AWS-Cost-Monitoring-Script
items.description: A Bash script designed to help users monitor and manage their AWS costs by providing automated insights into resource usage and cost breakdowns. It enables cost optimisation by offering real-time data analysis, helping users identify areas for potential savings and better budget management.

items.name: Onchain-Tic-Tac-Toe
items.description: Onchain Tic-Tac-Toe is a decentralized tic-tac-toe game implemented on Solidity. Players can challenge each other, make moves, and verify results on the blockchain. The game ensures fairness and transparency, allowing anyone to play without third-party interference.
